    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overtime Anomaly</strong> 是一款心理恐怖游戏，在空荡荡的办公楼里，你要熬过一周的加班，完成工作任务。但随着夜晚的深入，你开始察觉到一些... 不对劲的地方...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227190/extras/8252c99dfb29855ee11ae39af0dea238.poster.avif?t=1755270010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227190/extras/8252c99dfb29855ee11ae39af0dea238.webm?t=1755270010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227190/extras/8252c99dfb29855ee11ae39af0dea238.mp4?t=1755270010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能活过这一周，并最终获得老板承诺的升职吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227190/extras/a504aa048b87ca2eba6a1a983090ddfe.poster.avif?t=1755270010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227190/extras/a504aa048b87ca2eba6a1a983090ddfe.webm?t=1755270010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227190/extras/a504aa048b87ca2eba6a1a983090ddfe.mp4?t=1755270010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >观察周围环境，完成每日任务，报告任何异常现象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227190/extras/8e2b2894fb24a9d3a71a2e7ba4a23cda.poster.avif?t=1755270010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227190/extras/8e2b2894fb24a9